art), it is probably the closest thing to what I want.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlthough, because I was unable to get it to work, I am starting to work on a mod instead.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDid you have the latest version of FireSpitter installed (latest for whatever version of KSP you are playing)?\u00A0 Because that part depends on Firespitter to work\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"FrostBird347","CreatedById":197409,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-12-03T12:52:02Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223712803\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022190111\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221575370995\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022129964\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022linuxgurugamer\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, linuxgurugamer said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDid you have the latest version of FireSpitter installed (latest for whatever version of KSP you are playing)?\u00A0 Because that part depends on Firespitter to work\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNo, I did not have firespitter installed, testing it again with firespitter works, but I might make a few changes (removing everything except for the info drive and I am planning to attempt to allow kerbals in eva to view, but not edit it)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}